      <textAnnotation id="sid-C7DCDB1D-D64B-4EFB-A909-E57B8E1D7E38" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Complete or Partial expedite based on agreement with customer</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-02FE0B49-BCF0-4B17-9EFB-657E4F9312EF" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Create Separate Order with “Expedite fee” as a MMID tagged to Service Item with Manual reference to Original SO in Free Text Field 
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-ACABD024-376E-4E05-A822-A6BAF593A70F" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Manual Vs automatics pricing condition types
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-6DE48C13-9703-4862-9A84-6A6F4B59B653" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Preloaded condition types
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-4FD916AE-8764-4DAE-A306-432B9DCF201F" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>On new RDD on existing line item
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-DF9FD752-4A73-48EC-8E2B-EC9E3463AC36" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Alignment of expedite fee post goods issue based on Actual Delivery date &amp; T&amp;Cs</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-383EEC94-F7EC-4BC7-8C41-286D60E77965" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>New CDD (CBA can be override CDD manually)
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-1F520041-5D8F-46DB-B22F-944B6D5ECFD2" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>CBA to communicate revised CDD and expedite fee
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-460A88C2-6559-4225-AE3B-420713162546" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Review original expedited order to confirm shipment of Goods to customer and remove hold on order
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-10245780-68BD-4F37-8A2F-BF84B6073791" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>DR: Customer (Account Receivable}
CR:  Sales Revenue
Cr . Taxes (if applicable)
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-87EF940F-41D1-4A1C-9B13-852FCD006CA9" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>This entry will be technically cleared as per standard SAP functionality
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-8C7A5B7E-6062-4B6A-BCFF-B53645C9BAD9" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text> DR: Customer (Account Receivable}
CR:  Sales Revenue
Cr . Taxes (if applicable)
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-F43AC6DE-4E63-44D2-87BC-8AA6671C0D05" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text> DR: Customer (Accounts Receivable)
CR:  Customer (Account Receivable)
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-F6D96D4F-B05F-426F-9614-B3293A548C93" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>DR: Main Bank Account
